@DATABASE "High Steel"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - H - High Steel"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - H
                   ====================================

                                High Steel
                                ==========


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(30096,255)"}          30096,x (x= 1-255)
@{"Infinite Lives" rxs "address command zxampoke(30462,0)"}          30462,0
@{"Level = x     " rxs "address command zxampoke(30101,1)"}          30101,x (x= 1-??)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).



                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
